 class=usertitle>Wee Little Hunter</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#871F78>(8/4/02 12:59:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=175.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsdown.gif" align=absmiddle>  Luclin and poor loot</span><hr size=1> I guess this is a little thing that has ticked me off since spending $30 on Verants expansion pack.<br>
<br>
Why is it that most of the zones (of the ones I have been in) on Luclin have ZERO coins, and very little if any loot?  <br>
<br>
We pay big money for this expansion, and they give crap back.  I find myself now spending all my time at level 36 still in South Karana because thats one place I can make decent money to buy armor.  Even if it means killing some of the stuff that is green to me.<br>
<br>
At level 36, something better dang well be dropping off every monster in every zone.  I'd make more money in a level 1 newbie zone on Norrath than some of the Luclin zones.<br>
